1
00:00:00,501 --> 00:00:08,601
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,776 --> 00:00:17,013
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,251 --> 00:00:19,242
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,256 --> 00:00:26,022
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,093 --> 00:00:29,460
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,664 --> 00:00:33,225
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,601 --> 00:00:36,968
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:37,038 --> 00:00:44,467
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,545 --> 00:00:53,681
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,754 --> 00:01:01,786
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:02,029 --> 00:01:08,867
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,936 --> 00:01:17,002
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,311 --> 00:01:25,776
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,853 --> 00:01:27,878
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:34,739 --> 00:01:37,503
You shouldn't lower your guard, Sensei.

16
00:01:41,479 --> 00:01:45,506
I'll bury you and correct
old mistakes, now!

17
00:01:45,883 --> 00:01:50,217
Whatever you do now, it's too late...
I've won...

18
00:01:50,788 --> 00:01:52,688
The Leaf Village will crumble!

19
00:01:53,391 --> 00:01:58,795
I am the man who carried on the Leaf Will
of the First and Second Hokages...

20
00:01:59,764 --> 00:02:01,288
The Third Hokage!

21
00:02:02,267 --> 00:02:07,705
Orochimaru! Now I will perform an
ace Jutsu that even you don't know!

22
00:02:09,274 --> 00:02:11,708
Behold! Sealing jutsu!

23
00:02:12,477 --> 00:02:18,575
<i>Forbidden Secret Technique.</i>
<i>Reaper Death Seal!</i>

24
00:02:20,718 --> 00:02:22,743
<i>A Jutsu I don't know...</i>

25
00:02:40,471 --> 00:02:43,599
<i>Must hurry...</i>
<i>This darkness is dangerous.</i>

26
00:02:48,279 --> 00:02:49,906
I'll have you show it to me.

27
00:03:01,759 --> 00:03:02,987
What's the matter?

28
00:03:03,661 --> 00:03:07,427
Are you planning to be killed
slowly by your predecessors?

29
00:03:08,633 --> 00:03:11,500
Please perform that Jutsu, quick.

30
00:03:12,704 --> 00:03:13,864
<i>Not yet...?</i>

31
00:04:07,525 --> 00:04:10,426
It looks like... I was just in time.

32
00:04:11,329 --> 00:04:14,821
What's the matter?
You're already stumbling...

33
00:04:18,703 --> 00:04:22,298
<i>Now all that's left...</i>
<i>is to catch them!</i>

34
00:04:31,315 --> 00:04:32,339
<i>I got you!</i>

35
00:04:39,657 --> 00:04:41,386
<i>I won't let go!</i>

36
00:04:42,193 --> 00:04:43,319
<i>Appear!</i>

37
00:05:23,034 --> 00:05:26,265
<i>The darkness has disappeared...</i>
<i>What's this Jutsu?</i>

38
00:05:27,004 --> 00:05:27,993
Sarutobi!

39
00:05:43,754 --> 00:05:45,278
I'm sorry... Sarutobi...

40
00:05:49,961 --> 00:05:51,019
We caused you trouble...

41
00:05:54,065 --> 00:05:55,726
<i>Please forgive me...</i>

42
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:57,332
<i>Lord First Hokage!</i>

43
00:05:57,835 --> 00:05:59,268
<i>Lord Second Hokage!</i>

44
00:06:04,342 --> 00:06:05,673
<i>Seal!</i>

45
00:06:34,539 --> 00:06:36,302
Your own subordinates...!

46
00:06:46,784 --> 00:06:50,379
<i>All members in</i>
<i>the Leaf Village are a part of me.</i>

47
00:06:52,056 --> 00:06:55,787
<i>The villagers believe in me,</i>
<i>and I believe in everyone.</i>

48
00:06:56,694 --> 00:06:57,922
<i>That's what the Hokage is.</i>

49
00:06:59,196 --> 00:07:04,634
<i>Saru... Protect those who love</i>
<i>the village and believe in you.</i>

50
00:07:05,269 --> 00:07:09,865
<i>And bring them up as individuals</i>
<i>to whom you can leave the next era.</i>

51
00:07:11,842 --> 00:07:13,173
<i>As of tomorrow, you are the...</i>

52
00:07:15,580 --> 00:07:16,512
<i>Hokage!</i>

53
00:07:22,353 --> 00:07:26,517
Toying with even the lives
of your own subordinates...!

54
00:07:27,158 --> 00:07:30,924
Subordinates lives?
Stop the endless nonsense!

55
00:07:31,862 --> 00:07:36,231
Didn't these kids believed in you?

56
00:07:41,105 --> 00:07:43,073
Come! Enma!

57
00:07:57,855 --> 00:07:58,617
You're mine!

58
00:07:59,624 --> 00:08:00,784
Striking Shadow Snake!

59
00:08:02,994 --> 00:08:03,983
Dang it! You little...!

60
00:08:07,498 --> 00:08:08,658
It's over!

61
00:08:22,380 --> 00:08:24,405
<i>What is this sensation...?</i>

62
00:08:24,882 --> 00:08:26,315
<i>This is bad...</i>

63
00:08:39,730 --> 00:08:40,719
- Die!
- Die!

64
00:09:01,652 --> 00:09:03,381
We have to hold them off here somehow.

65
00:09:04,321 --> 00:09:05,549
Isn't our back up here yet?!

66
00:09:10,494 --> 00:09:11,426
<i>This is out of our hands!</i>

67
00:09:16,834 --> 00:09:21,168
Ninja Art: Summoning
Bring Down the House Jutsu!

68
00:09:31,849 --> 00:09:32,838
This Jutsu...

69
00:09:37,722 --> 00:09:39,747
Long time no see, Ibiki.

70
00:09:40,357 --> 00:09:43,520
Jeez, is that body
the only thing that grew?!

71
00:09:43,694 --> 00:09:45,491
I can't stand to look!

72
00:09:46,464 --> 00:09:47,453
Master Jiraiya...

73
00:09:47,898 --> 00:09:50,389
Jiraiya...! One of Sannin,
the three legendary Shinobi?!

74
00:09:50,634 --> 00:09:56,368
Peeps, open up those little eyes
of yours just this once and observe well.

75
00:10:01,345 --> 00:10:02,869
How wonderful!

76
00:10:02,947 --> 00:10:08,010
The devil region beyond heaven
of Jiraiya, the fantastic sage Ninja...

77
00:10:10,554 --> 00:10:13,751
will rage!

78
00:10:16,794 --> 00:10:20,753
Snakes that have been antagonized
by the frog. Begone!

79
00:10:23,734 --> 00:10:26,828
<i>So that Orochimaru has finally started, eh?</i>

80
00:10:29,907 --> 00:10:30,874
Where's the Third Hokage?

81
00:10:32,042 --> 00:10:33,100
The Exam arena.

82
00:10:35,212 --> 00:10:36,076
I see...

83
00:10:38,315 --> 00:10:40,146
<i>Don't die...old man.</i>

84
00:11:38,042 --> 00:11:40,567
Why... didn't you dodge?

85
00:11:45,750 --> 00:11:46,682
Dang it!

86
00:11:48,219 --> 00:11:50,016
The Reaper Death Seal...

87
00:11:50,488 --> 00:11:52,581
In this Sealing Jutsu,

88
00:11:53,491 --> 00:11:55,982
in exchange for the effectiveness
of Jutsu...

89
00:11:56,561 --> 00:12:00,156
one's own soul is handed over
to the Grim Reaper.

90
00:12:00,732 --> 00:12:03,462
It's a Jutsu that costs your life...

91
00:12:07,705 --> 00:12:09,536
<i>My Jutsu doesn't activate...</i>

92
00:12:10,274 --> 00:12:14,734
There's no need to dodge.
I will die, anyway.

93
00:12:16,347 --> 00:12:20,681
At the same time the Sealing ends,
my soul will also be devoured.

94
00:12:21,953 --> 00:12:24,649
It's a Jutsu of the hero
who once saved this village.

95
00:12:25,022 --> 00:12:29,049
From now, you will also die...
by this Jutsu!

96
00:12:29,460 --> 00:12:34,830
So this Jutsu also sealed
that Nine-Tailed Fox., huh?!

97
00:12:37,135 --> 00:12:43,597
And now, your soul will be dragged out...
and sealed!

98
00:12:45,176 --> 00:12:47,235
<i>My body...won't listen to what I say!</i>

99
00:12:52,984 --> 00:12:55,316
You'll probably be able to see it soon.

100
00:12:56,020 --> 00:13:01,583
Your soul is also already
about halfway out, so.

101
00:13:02,326 --> 00:13:06,353
Those who have their souls sealed
by this Jutsu

102
00:13:06,431 --> 00:13:09,594
will suffer inside the belly
of the Grim Reaper for eternity

103
00:13:09,667 --> 00:13:12,932
and will never attain peace...

104
00:13:13,938 --> 00:13:19,774
Those who seal and are sealed
have their souls intertwined,

105
00:13:19,844 --> 00:13:24,941
and will hate each other,
and continue to battle for eternity!

106
00:13:32,457 --> 00:13:33,355
What...?!

107
00:14:00,251 --> 00:14:02,481
<i>This is... the Grim Reaper?!</i>

108
00:14:09,327 --> 00:14:14,264
Knock it off! You old dotard!
I won't let you do as you like.

109
00:14:31,883 --> 00:14:34,215
Hurry up and... die!

110
00:14:47,632 --> 00:14:49,691
Okay, everyone. Line up!

111
00:14:54,839 --> 00:14:56,272
Quiet, everyone!

112
00:14:57,708 --> 00:14:59,232
Konohamaru!

113
00:15:00,711 --> 00:15:03,179
Konohamaru, it's not going
to collapse, is it?

114
00:15:03,381 --> 00:15:05,440
It'II... it'll be okay.

115
00:15:06,083 --> 00:15:12,318
The structure of this face rock path is old,
but is of strong construction.

116
00:15:13,758 --> 00:15:16,192
My grandpa said so before.

117
00:15:19,864 --> 00:15:23,698
So it'll definitely be okay.

118
00:15:30,575 --> 00:15:31,303
Someone's coming!

119
00:15:32,643 --> 00:15:33,507
Which one...?

120
00:15:36,180 --> 00:15:37,147
Uchiha, huh?

121
00:15:38,049 --> 00:15:39,175
<i>Then, what about Temari?</i>

122
00:15:52,163 --> 00:15:53,562
Don't run away like that...

123
00:15:55,466 --> 00:15:56,728
Fine.

124
00:15:59,904 --> 00:16:03,340
I'll be your opponent this time.

125
00:16:03,874 --> 00:16:04,841
Wait!

126
00:16:07,712 --> 00:16:08,906
Temari!

127
00:16:10,081 --> 00:16:11,981
I assumed you'd been
creamed by him.

128
00:16:12,817 --> 00:16:13,749
So you're okay?!

129
00:16:16,187 --> 00:16:17,916
Yeah. Somehow...

130
00:16:19,156 --> 00:16:19,850
But...

131
00:16:22,393 --> 00:16:24,088
it didn't turn out to
be much of a delay.

132
00:16:24,662 --> 00:16:28,098
No, it's time necessary for
Gaara's recovery.

133
00:16:29,166 --> 00:16:32,135
Besides, it'll lead to
his consumption of Chakra.

134
00:16:53,257 --> 00:16:53,916
This is...

135
00:16:54,525 --> 00:16:55,822
Shampoo, again?

136
00:16:56,927 --> 00:16:58,554
No, it's Sasuke.

137
00:17:01,165 --> 00:17:04,862
There are several smells near him.
He caught up...

138
00:17:06,570 --> 00:17:07,366
At last...

139
00:17:11,876 --> 00:17:12,604
Sasuke.

140
00:17:15,846 --> 00:17:17,973
He's totally stopped moving

141
00:17:18,049 --> 00:17:19,346
Is he going to fight with them?!

142
00:17:21,852 --> 00:17:22,682
<i>Sasuke...</i>

143
00:17:23,454 --> 00:17:24,352
Let's hurry!

144
00:17:27,591 --> 00:17:32,290
<i>What's this clump of countless smells</i>
<i>coming from another direction?</i>

145
00:17:33,464 --> 00:17:37,332
Hey! There's something besides us
tracking Sasuke!

146
00:17:37,735 --> 00:17:38,360
What?!

147
00:17:39,070 --> 00:17:40,833
An enemy? An ally?!

148
00:17:41,706 --> 00:17:43,901
I don't know. But...

149
00:17:44,475 --> 00:17:45,100
But?

150
00:17:47,545 --> 00:17:48,705
It's not human.

151
00:17:49,113 --> 00:17:49,636
<i>Huh?!</i>

152
00:17:50,181 --> 00:17:50,943
<i>Huh?!</i>

153
00:17:59,356 --> 00:18:02,655
Go! Kankuro! I'll take him again...

154
00:18:07,765 --> 00:18:10,700
Temari, you take Gaara
and go on ahead.

155
00:18:10,901 --> 00:18:11,526
What?

156
00:18:12,503 --> 00:18:14,164
You're at your limit...

157
00:18:15,506 --> 00:18:17,633
I don't need a hindrance.

158
00:18:17,942 --> 00:18:18,567
But...!

159
00:18:19,176 --> 00:18:19,835
Go!

160
00:18:28,419 --> 00:18:29,181
Hurry up and go

161
00:18:31,822 --> 00:18:32,550
Okay...

162
00:18:34,458 --> 00:18:38,360
It can't be helped...
I'll be your opponent!

163
00:18:41,365 --> 00:18:43,299
Humph! I don't care who it is!

164
00:18:43,768 --> 00:18:44,496
No!

165
00:18:48,973 --> 00:18:50,804
Your opponent is me!

166
00:18:55,379 --> 00:18:56,243
You...!

167
00:18:58,449 --> 00:18:59,211
Shino?

168
00:19:00,050 --> 00:19:01,540
Why are you here?!

169
00:19:04,588 --> 00:19:08,922
I put a female beetle on you
before you left the arena.

170
00:19:10,427 --> 00:19:12,895
The females have almost no smell...

171
00:19:14,331 --> 00:19:19,200
Only a male can sniff out
the subtle smell of the female.

172
00:19:20,037 --> 00:19:22,870
Though the male itself
has a strong smell...

173
00:19:28,345 --> 00:19:31,280
Sasuke Uchiha...
You pursue Gaara.

174
00:19:32,249 --> 00:19:36,583
Because the battle between you
and him hasn't been settled yet.

175
00:19:40,057 --> 00:19:46,121
I'll fight him, because originally
I was his opponent...

176
00:19:46,730 --> 00:19:49,927
<i>I withdraw!</i>
<i>Please go ahead with the match.</i>

177
00:19:55,306 --> 00:19:57,001
Leave this to me here! Go!

178
00:20:00,377 --> 00:20:02,902
You're very confident.
But are you going to be okay?

179
00:20:05,115 --> 00:20:06,207
No need to worry.

180
00:20:07,084 --> 00:20:10,019
I'll go back you up if
I have just ten minutes.

181
00:20:11,021 --> 00:20:13,922
Humph. By then, I'll be done too.

182
00:20:25,469 --> 00:20:28,836
None of you know anything at all.

183
00:20:29,673 --> 00:20:35,009
You guys probably don't know
of the real terror of this world.

184
00:20:37,781 --> 00:20:43,185
In that case...
you'll teach me that terror?

185
00:20:45,990 --> 00:20:46,752
No...

186
00:20:47,725 --> 00:20:51,661
If you defeat me and chase Gaara,
you'll be forced to know.

187
00:20:52,429 --> 00:20:55,057
That is, only <i>if</i> you can defeat me.

188
00:21:05,910 --> 00:21:15,979
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

189
00:21:16,420 --> 00:21:27,263
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

190
00:21:37,374 --> 00:21:43,006
<i>Yes, breathe in the air</i>
<i>Lift your face to the sky and jump</i>

191
00:21:43,080 --> 00:21:48,040
<i>If it rains, take a break</i>
<i>Go where the wind takes you</i>

192
00:21:48,419 --> 00:21:53,322
<i>So many regrets</i>
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>

193
00:21:53,390 --> 00:21:58,521
<i>Let's go carve the badges in our chest</i>
<i>Yes, it's Show Time, life begins now.</i>

194
00:21:58,596 --> 00:22:08,767
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

195
00:22:09,073 --> 00:22:19,506
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

196
00:22:19,583 --> 00:22:30,152
<i>Transform sadness into the wind</i>
<i>and continue to forge on</i>

197
00:22:30,227 --> 00:22:35,790
<i>Forge on strong</i>

198
00:22:46,977 --> 00:22:50,640
You who are strong...
You who are called Uchiha...

199
00:22:51,182 --> 00:22:54,845
You who have friends...
You who have a purpose...

200
00:22:55,653 --> 00:22:58,349
You who are like me...

201
00:22:59,623 --> 00:23:03,150
By killing you, I can truly exist!

202
00:23:04,028 --> 00:23:10,627
Uchiha, you are my prey!

203
00:23:11,302 --> 00:23:13,600
Next time: "Astonishing Truth!
Gaara's Identity Emerges!"
